{"tid":524291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"80後記唔記得當年小學會比老師打手板?","createTime":"2018-01-09T12:18:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T12:35:31.000Z","uid":25345,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"578b42c14278185fe28a23bb9a885c452454e08c","tid":524291,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T12:18:33.000Z","msg":"諗起都痴撚線,仆街一把木尺狠狠咁打落黎,有時仲打幾下<br />\n痛撚到標眼水,有時仲痛幾日,點解個時咁都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12338a976e1e9594b7137dd19fdd7e0ad100fb06","tid":524291,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T12:23:48.000Z","msg":"當年被老師用雞毛掃打多，其實雞毛掃唔算太痛，不過有一個老師鍾意用1cm厚塑膠間尺打，真心痛到癲"},{"pid":"02b997bab9d37793bc7263407bd61574a10554dc","tid":524291,"uid":91432,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T12:24:30.000Z","msg":"九十後表示幼稚園老師都會打手板"},{"pid":"585bd951f8947a7cf91eaadb3332a5cc02fdd783","tid":524291,"uid":96472,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T12:28:30.000Z","msg":"以前排隊打手板，我地成班成日縮<br />\n結果打得仲甘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前教數學果個係訓導，打手就用成米長果d 打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2989725d9717a16b9047a7dc7096c76b012e993e","tid":524291,"uid":154385,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T12:31:22.000Z","msg":"90後小學藤條打孖上"},{"pid":"c314e0828be75bbe13e05e57fd9420cde029fac0","tid":524291,"uid":40550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:04:43.000Z","msg":"而家應該一打就比人告到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a3f171da9f1ee544dc67b9482f541bd7e8b408","tid":524291,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:07:14.000Z","msg":"見過小學同班同學同英文主任用1 CM 厚既間尺打手板<br />\n<br />